@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userId = 7a26f2f7-2d21-4c56-954f-56449b8998e0

### ================================================================
###                    1. PAYMENT CONTROLLER
### ================================================================

### 1.1 Solicitar um novo pagamento (Request Payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "valuePaid": 150.00,
  "cardHolderName": "MATHEUS TORRES",
  "cardNumber": "1234567812345678",
  "expirationDate": "12/28",
  "cvv": "123",
  "recurrence": false
}

### 1.2 Listar todos os pagamentos de um usuário (getAllPayments)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/payments?page=0&size=10&sort=paymentRequestDate,desc
Accept: application/json

### 1.3 Listar pagamentos com filtros (Specification)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/payments?paymentControl=EFFECTED
Accept: application/json
